Viceroy Duanfang wants you
to take a look as well.

288
00:20:06,290 --> 00:20:08,290
Governor Enming of Anhui has passed away?

289
00:20:08,290 --> 00:20:08,900
Yes.

290
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:10,580
Things have got extremely serious.

291
00:20:10,580 --> 00:20:12,140
