the rebel leader, Xu Xilin, alive

292
00:20:12,140 --> 00:20:14,100
around 4 a.m. after their defeat.

293
00:20:14,100 --> 00:20:14,970
The Grand Council Minister

294
00:20:14,970 --> 00:20:15,970
instructed Viceroy Duanfang

295
00:20:15,970 --> 00:20:17,580
to quell the unrest in the south

296
00:20:17,580 --> 00:20:19,910
by executing Xu Xilin as soon as possible.

297
00:20:21,620 --> 00:20:22,210
Well...

298
00:20:22,580 --> 00:20:24,250
Send a telegram to Anqing immediately.

299
00:20:24,250 --> 00:20:25,790
No need for
further interrogation of Criminal Xu.

300
00:20:25,790 --> 00:20:27,100
Execute him as soon as possible.

301
00:20:27,100 --> 00:20:27,860
Understood.

302
00:20:27,970 --> 00:20:29,830
I'm going to draft the notice now.

303
00:20:30,690 --> 00:20:31,750
Viceroy Duanfang.

304
00:20:32,940 --> 00:20:34,860
For things like this,
you should be ruthless

305
00:20:34,860 --> 00:20:36,530
and show no mercy.

306
00:20:36,690 --> 00:20:37,100
Sir,

307
00:20:37,820 --> 00:20:38,950
maybe you are right.

308
00:20:39,210 --> 00:20:40,340
But I think we should

309
00:20:40,530 --> 00:20:41,140
interrogate

310
00:20:41,140 --> 00:20:42,870
Xu Xilin first even if there are

311
00:20:43,140 --> 00:20:44,870
enough reasons to execute him.

312
00:20:44,970 --> 00:20:46,210
Stop being such a stubborn scholar.

313
00:20:46,210 --> 00:20:46,970
Tufang,

314
00:20:47,460 --> 00:20:49,940
the rebellion in Anqing
is spreading like wildfire.

315
00:20:49,940 --> 00:20:52,010
We've found Xu's accomplices

316
00:20:52,010 --> 00:20:54,690
across a dozen counties
in Shaoxing, Zhejiang.

317
00:20:54,730 --> 00:20:55,860
We have to adopt

318
00:20:55,860 --> 00:20:57,490
special methods before the chaos erupts.

319
00:20:57,490 --> 00:21:00,970
Otherwise, the consequences
will be devastating.

320
00:21:08,040 --> 00:21:10,460
[On July 6, 1907, Xu Xilin,
the Restoration Society's member,]

321
00:21:10,460 --> 00:21:12,880
[the Anhui Police Office's Vice Director,
the Police Academy's Supervisor,]

322
00:21:12,910 --> 00:21:16,710
[assassinated Governor Enming of Anhui
in Anqing, and led the students to revolt]

323
00:21:16,710 --> 00:21:20,520
[and occupy the armory. He was captured
and killed after a four-hour-long battle.]

