329
00:21:49,420 --> 00:21:52,900
♪ To devote myself to the state ♪

330
00:21:52,900 --> 00:21:58,100
♪ I'll keep that in mind ♪

331
00:21:58,580 --> 00:22:07,010
Bravo! Bravo!

332
00:22:07,490 --> 00:22:09,100
♪ Fine ♪

333
00:22:09,490 --> 00:22:11,490
♪ Given your exceptional martial skills ♪

334
00:22:11,490 --> 00:22:13,860
♪ And the guts ♪

335
00:22:13,970 --> 00:22:16,820
♪ I'll step back and let you go ♪

