00:22:29,970 --> 00:22:31,340
♪ Yes, Father ♪

342
00:22:31,980 --> 00:22:34,240
Sir, you're not enjoying the opera. Why?

343
00:22:35,820 --> 00:22:37,750
"What's the point of taking a seat?

344
00:22:38,010 --> 00:22:40,100
Bird's tongue tea and old Yue opera."

345
00:22:40,340 --> 00:22:41,860
"Help yourself to some snacks.

346
00:22:41,860 --> 00:22:43,970
Lard buns and poussin."

347
00:22:46,860 --> 00:22:48,690
I've come from Shanghai.

348
00:22:50,100 --> 00:22:51,620
Master Sun guided me here

349
00:22:52,140 --> 00:22:55,940
for the views of the mountains, rivers,
and incense halls in Fuyang.

350
00:22:58,580 --> 00:23:01,340
May I ask which mountain
you're here for, sir?

351
00:23:03,210 --> 00:23:05,340
The Chinese Mountain.

352
00:23:05,860 --> 00:23:07,100
And the river?

353
00:23:07,940 --> 00:23:09,600
The Han-rejuvenating River.

354
00:23:09,860 --> 00:23:11,390
And what about the incense?

355
00:23:11,620 --> 00:23:12,730
The patriotic incense.

356
00:23:12,730 --> 00:23:13,970
What hall?

357
00:23:14,860 --> 00:23:16,260
The Hall of Restoration.

358
00:23:26,620 --> 00:23:28,970
You are indeed Master Sun's friend.

359
00:23:29,730 --> 00:23:31,340
So who are you, sir?

360
00:23:31,620 --> 00:23:33,740
Sun Jingchao's private advisor.

361
00:23:42,030 --> 00:23:47,380
Bravo! Bravo!

362
00:23:47,850 --> 00:23:49,720
I've been waiting in Fuyang for seven days.

363
00:23:49,030 --> 00:23:54,390
[Incense Hall of the White Cloth Party]

364
00:23:50,210 --> 00:23:50,970
Advisor,

365
00:23:51,430 --> 00:23:54,540
you've finally shown yourself.

366
00:23:58,140 --> 00:23:59,860
I wanted to see true sincerity.

367
00:23:59,860 --> 00:24:02,210
It's just that in this world,

368
00:24:02,210 --> 00:24:05,490
there are too many liars
peddling their fake solutions.

369
00:24:05,970 --> 00:24:07,790
Do I look like one of them?

370
00:24:09,450 --> 00:24:11,450
Even if you're,

371
00:24:11,580 --> 00:24:12,970
I won't be surprised.

372
00:24:13,730 --> 00:24:15,970
Nowadays, everyone in the court

373
00:24:16,210 --> 00:24:17,830
is like that, right?

374
00:24:20,140 --> 00:24:24,210
Fine Song-Yuan enlightening texts,
gold and jade Buddhas,

375
00:24:25,380 --> 00:24:29,690
heirloom pills, secret ointments.

376
00:24:30,490 --> 00:24:31,730
Everyone claims that

377
00:24:31,730 --> 00:24:33,490
their goal is to save us common people

378
00:24:33,490 --> 00:24:35,380
from our dire straits.

379
00:24:35,380 --> 00:24:37,860
But I think the worst one

380
00:24:37,970 --> 00:24:41,380
is the so-called new policy.

381
00:24:43,660 --> 00:24:45,110
You're so sharp, sir.

382
00:24:47,010 --> 00:24:48,770
It sounds so good.

383
00:24:49,620 --> 00:24:50,860
Don't you think so?

384
00:24:51,360 --> 00:24:53,500
Abolish the Imperial Exam,
establish new schools,

385
00:24:53,500 --> 00:24:55,720
switch to constitutionalism,
and train new armies.

386
00:24:55,720 --> 00:24:57,070
They all

387
00:24:57,100 --> 00:24:59,380
sound amazing.

388
00:24:59,730 --> 00:25:02,580
But I just have one question.

389
00:25:03,140 --> 00:25:05,100
Which of these

390
00:25:05,730 --> 00:25:07,140
doesn't cost money?

391
00:25:07,690 --> 00:25:09,210
They all need a large amount of money!

392
00:25:09,210 --> 00:25:11,010
Yes, exactly!

393
00:25:11,010 --> 00:25:12,410
You're insightful, sir.

394
00:25:13,940 --> 00:25:15,380
Then tell me

395
00:25:15,820 --> 00:25:19,620
where to get the money
for this new policy.

396
00:25:22,620 --> 00:25:23,340
It's from us,

397
00:25:23,340 --> 00:25:25,140
the poor people,

398
00:25:25,620 --> 00:25:26,490
isn't it?

399
00:25:26,490 --> 00:25:28,210
Yes, it is.

400
00:25:29,620 --> 00:25:30,680
And think about it.

401
00:25:31,210 --> 00:25:32,690
Since the new policy was implemented,

402
00:25:32,690 --> 00:25:35,420
how many new taxes
has the government collected?

403
00:25:36,100 --> 00:25:37,940
What kind of new policy is that?

404
00:25:38,730 --> 00:25:40,660
All the benefits go to the court,

405
00:25:40,970 --> 00:25:43,230
yet only we, the poor people, are paying!

406
00:25:43,230 --> 00:25:44,710
Does that make sense?

407
00:25:45,100 --> 00:25:46,380
Indeed!

408
00:25:46,380 --> 00:25:48,100
It's so unreasonable!

409
00:25:49,100 --> 00:25:51,420
Let's talk about something else, Mr. Wu.

410
00:25:51,810 --> 00:25:54,000
My son used to study at a private school

411
00:25:54,020 --> 00:25:55,100
in the village,

412
00:25:55,100 --> 00:25:56,860
which didn't cost much.

413
00:25:57,490 --> 00:26:00,490
Now he's gone
to public school in the city,

414
00:26:00,490 --> 00:26:02,620
with expenses covering
food, accommodation,

415
00:26:02,620 --> 00:26:03,990
and tuition.

416
00:26:04,340 --> 00:26:06,970
It's suddenly several times
more expensive.

417
00:26:07,040 --> 00:26:08,500
Without money for school,

418
00:26:08,860 --> 00:26:10,490
there's no path
to an official career either.

419
00:26:10,490 --> 00:26:12,450
Tell me where my son can go.

420
00:26:12,590 --> 00:26:15,700
Where will life take him? Huh?

421
00:26:15,730 --> 00:26:17,970
He'll have to come back to his father

422
00:26:18,110 --> 00:26:20,080
and join the White Cloth Party

423
00:26:20,350 --> 00:26:22,110
for rebellion, right?

424
00:26:22,540 --> 00:26:24,060
Indeed.

425
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:26,030
Therefore,

426
00:26:27,210 --> 00:26:29,450
for those peddlers
of their fake solutions,

427
00:26:29,450 --> 00:26:30,710
my proposition is that

428
00:26:31,340 --> 00:26:33,820
whether they're humans or ghosts,

429
00:26:33,820 --> 00:26:35,010
ancient or modern,

430
00:26:35,010 --> 00:26:37,070
or which ancient classic they quote,

431
00:26:37,860 --> 00:26:39,380
we should take down all of them!

432
00:26:39,380 --> 00:26:41,100
Right, take them down!

433
00:26:41,100 --> 00:26:43,700
Take them down!
Take them down! Take them down!

434
00:26:45,970 --> 00:26:46,820
Dewy-eyed,

435
00:26:47,250 --> 00:26:48,850
why are you back at this hour?

436
00:26:49,250 --> 00:26:50,210
Mrs. Qiu Jin sent me over

437
00:26:50,210 --> 00:26:51,010
from Datong Academy

438
00:26:51,010 --> 00:26:52,620
to deliver a message overnight.

439
00:26:52,620 --> 00:26:53,680
What's the matter?

440
00:26:53,690 --> 00:26:55,180
Something big has happened.

441
00:26:55,180 --> 00:26:55,660
Mrs. Qiu Jin

442
00:26:55,660 --> 00:26:56,820
saw the newspaper in Shanghai

443
00:26:56,820 --> 00:26:58,490
that reported the incident in Anqing.

444
00:26:58,490 --> 00:27:00,620
Xu Xilin has been killed.

445
00:27:03,620 --> 00:27:05,250
Mrs. Qiu Jin was
overwhelmed by great agony.

446
00:27:05,250 --> 00:27:07,820
She didn't eat, speak, or give any orders.

447
00:27:08,140 --> 00:27:09,970
Later, she obliterated
the secret documents

448
00:27:09,970 --> 00:27:10,580
as well as

449
00:27:10,580 --> 00:27:12,210
the Restoration Society's telegrams.

450
00:27:12,210 --> 00:27:14,140
She also hid the academy's firearms,

451
00:27:14,140 --> 00:27:14,860
ordering the students

452
00:27:14,860 --> 00:27:16,320
to disperse and relocate.

453
00:27:16,730 --> 00:27:18,580
She said the uprising plan had been leaked

454
00:27:18,580 --> 00:27:19,820
and asked Mr. Wu and the Advisor

455
00:27:19,820 --> 00:27:20,860
to make Plan B immediately

456
00:27:20,860 --> 00:27:22,320
to preserve our strength.

457
00:27:22,420 --> 00:27:23,100
The government troops

458
00:27:23,100 --> 00:27:25,160
in Hangzhou could attack at any time.

459
00:27:27,100 --> 00:27:27,970
Then

460
00:27:28,730 --> 00:27:30,970
did Qiu Jin herself move to a safe place?

461
00:27:34,050 --> 00:27:35,450
She ignored everyone's advice

462
00:27:35,450 --> 00:27:37,450
and insisted on guarding the academy.

463
00:27:37,450 --> 00:27:39,100
In the end, Datong Academy was

464
00:27:39,100 --> 00:27:41,250
surrounded by soldiers two hours later.

465
00:27:41,250 --> 00:27:42,250
Qiu Jin

466
00:27:42,480 --> 00:27:43,540
has been arrested.

467
00:27:47,890 --> 00:27:50,810
[On July 10, 1997,
Qiu Jin heard about Xu Xilin's failure.]

468
00:27:50,810 --> 00:27:53,730
[She sent everyone away and chose
to stay at Datong Academy herself.]

469
00:27:53,750 --> 00:27:56,770
