00:28:20,970 --> 00:28:21,970
Make way!

474
00:28:22,100 --> 00:28:23,360
Hey! Move! Step aside!

475
00:28:23,970 --> 00:28:25,730
Listen up, everyone!

476
00:28:26,340 --> 00:28:27,100
To assist with

477
00:28:27,100 --> 00:28:28,940
the arrest of the rebels,

478
00:28:29,380 --> 00:28:30,760
all boats and ships

479
00:28:30,940 --> 00:28:32,620
from Anqing and Shaoxing

