494
00:29:42,860 --> 00:29:44,390
To the Qinghe Qinlou Villa.

495
00:29:44,420 --> 00:29:45,030
Okay!

496
00:29:47,360 --> 00:29:50,370
[Shanghai Qinghe Qinlou Villa]

497
00:29:59,210 --> 00:30:00,420
Take it to her room.

498
00:30:04,340 --> 00:30:05,860
