503
00:30:12,030 --> 00:30:12,780
that year?

504
00:30:12,860 --> 00:30:13,860
Wasn't it just...

505
00:30:13,950 --> 00:30:16,280
Do you have to bring up the worst topics?

506
00:30:18,490 --> 00:30:20,340
Could she be involved

507
00:30:20,360 --> 00:30:22,880
in the rebellion in Anqing and Shaoxing?

508
00:30:23,010 --> 00:30:24,310
Are you done?

509
00:30:25,970 --> 00:30:28,230
No matter what, she's just a frail woman.

510
00:30:31,340 --> 00:30:32,940
Have you read the newspaper?

511
00:30:33,660 --> 00:30:34,690
The media in Shanghai

512
00:30:34,690 --> 00:30:37,220
is unanimously lashing out
at the court this time

513
00:30:37,220 --> 00:30:38,970
for the cruel execution
of beheading Qiu Jin,

514
00:30:38,970 --> 00:30:40,380
the woman from Shaoxing.

515
00:30:42,620 --> 00:30:44,210
Qiu (lit. autumn) Jin.

516
00:30:45,530 --> 00:30:47,770
Autumn wind, autumn rain,

517
00:30:48,900 --> 00:30:50,490
how distressful.

518
00:32:46,450 --> 00:32:47,180
Yihua.

