00:32:48,050 --> 00:32:48,820
Yihua?

520
00:32:50,290 --> 00:32:51,420
I'm here, over here!

521
00:32:55,100 --> 00:32:56,040
Baoquan,

522
00:32:56,620 --> 00:32:57,730
