after this chaos dies down.

557
00:34:25,969 --> 00:34:27,130
The breakfast

558
00:34:27,699 --> 00:34:29,830
indeed has a unique flavor in this way.

559
00:34:48,699 --> 00:34:49,659
Shuhong.

560
00:34:50,679 --> 00:34:51,900
What's this for?

561
00:34:53,780 --> 00:34:55,580
