00:35:00,220 --> 00:35:01,940
We can take photos at home too?

565
00:35:03,020 --> 00:35:04,340
Then I should go get dressed up first.

566
00:35:04,340 --> 00:35:06,170
Or I won't look great in the camera.

567
00:35:06,170 --> 00:35:07,260
This is good!

568
00:35:07,340 --> 00:35:09,220
Keep it real and comfy
when we take photos at home.

569
00:35:09,220 --> 00:35:10,280
It's a candid shot.

570
00:35:13,530 --> 00:35:14,340
Shuhong,

571
00:35:14,850 --> 00:35:16,850
how about I go get another round fan?

572
00:35:18,700 --> 00:35:19,650
Let me help you.

573
00:35:25,340 --> 00:35:26,070
Here you are.

574
00:35:27,790 --> 00:35:29,590
How elegant this painted fan is!

575
00:35:30,700 --> 00:35:32,100
There's even a poem on it.

576
00:35:36,130 --> 00:35:39,610
"If life could remain
the way it was when we first met.

577
00:35:39,970 --> 00:35:43,700
There would be no grief
over the past on the painted fan."

578
00:35:44,010 --> 00:35:45,010
What does it mean?

579
00:35:46,050 --> 00:35:47,170
It means

580
00:35:47,950 --> 00:35:49,010
if only life could stay

581
00:35:49,010 --> 00:35:50,490
at the moment when lovers

582
00:35:50,490 --> 00:35:51,260
first meet.

583
00:35:51,780 --> 00:35:53,010
Then there wouldn't be

584
00:35:53,010 --> 00:35:55,170
any heartbreak or drama that comes after.

585
00:35:55,170 --> 00:35:55,740
Elegant.

586
00:35:56,370 --> 00:35:58,970
The calligraphy is elegant,
and so is the poem.

587
00:36:00,610 --> 00:36:02,410
But it's just wishful thinking.

588
00:36:02,820 --> 00:36:04,090
No one can keep

589
00:36:04,420 --> 00:36:06,020
those good old days forever.

590
00:36:07,010 --> 00:36:07,940
Besides,

591
00:36:08,050 --> 00:36:09,710
when you first meet those men,

592
00:36:09,740 --> 00:36:10,780
they all hide

593
00:36:10,780 --> 00:36:11,970
their true colors,

594
00:36:12,060 --> 00:36:13,500
pretending to be caring

595
00:36:13,520 --> 00:36:14,770
and attentive.

596
00:36:15,320 --> 00:36:16,780
But once a man's got you as his woman,

597
00:36:16,780 --> 00:36:18,510
he's no longer the same person.

598
00:36:18,540 --> 00:36:20,970
Chairman Song wouldn't
treat you like that, would he?

599
00:36:20,970 --> 00:36:22,290
All men are tricky.

600
00:36:22,700 --> 00:36:23,900
They're all the same.

601
00:36:24,190 --> 00:36:25,920
Turn your face a bit to the side.

602
00:36:26,650 --> 00:36:28,710
Mrs. Song, you have a beautiful nose.

603
00:36:29,220 --> 00:36:30,620
Has anyone told you that?

604
00:36:32,420 --> 00:36:33,730
At my age,

605
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:35,820
no one would compliment me like that!

606
00:36:37,260 --> 00:36:38,460
Song Chen told me that

607
00:36:38,690 --> 00:36:39,520
your father's the owner

608
00:36:39,520 --> 00:36:41,650
of the largest flour mill in Shanghai.

609
00:36:43,260 --> 00:36:44,610
You and Song Chen

610
00:36:44,700 --> 00:36:46,130
have talked about me?

611
00:36:47,510 --> 00:36:49,640
I guess he just mentioned it casually.

612
00:36:55,300 --> 00:36:56,260
Shuhong,

613
00:36:57,010 --> 00:36:59,290
even today, I still can't figure it out.

614
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:00,250
Why did

615
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:02,180
someone like you, a gorgeous girl,

616
00:37:02,180 --> 00:37:03,050
end up getting involved

617
00:37:03,050 --> 00:37:04,700
in that bloody mess?

618
00:37:05,090 --> 00:37:06,700
It's so weird.

619
00:37:07,050 --> 00:37:08,420
Your family owns the decent,

620
00:37:08,420 --> 00:37:10,050
time-honored brand, the Kaiwentang.

621
00:37:10,050 --> 00:37:11,980
You could have led a carefree life.

622
00:37:12,010 --> 00:37:14,610
Your ancestors rest
in a spot of good feng shui.

623
00:37:15,340 --> 00:37:17,860
"There would be no grief
over the past on the painted fan." Right?

624
00:37:17,860 --> 00:37:18,340
Shuhong?

625
00:37:18,340 --> 00:37:19,210
Stay still.

626
00:37:19,490 --> 00:37:20,380
I'm going to take it.

627
00:37:20,380 --> 00:37:21,180
Look this way.

628
00:37:23,300 --> 00:37:24,010
Hold on.

629
00:37:26,970 --> 00:37:27,580
Good.

630
00:37:30,090 --> 00:37:30,570
Master.

631
00:37:39,450 --> 00:37:40,300
I've been to

632
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:41,700
the photography studios so many times,

633
00:37:41,700 --> 00:37:43,220
but haven't got one satisfactory photo.

634
00:37:43,220 --> 00:37:44,480
Guess this one you took

635
00:37:44,580 --> 00:37:46,110
is going to be weird as well.

636
00:37:48,310 --> 00:37:49,510
What makes you laugh?

637
00:37:49,860 --> 00:37:51,650
Baoquan, come here.

638
00:37:51,780 --> 00:37:52,490
Let Shuhong

639
00:37:52,490 --> 00:37:53,940
take a photo of you too.

640
00:37:54,130 --> 00:37:55,420
Come on, sit down.

641
00:37:55,700 --> 00:37:56,270
Here.

642
00:37:56,850 --> 00:37:57,970
Alright.

643
00:37:58,720 --> 00:37:59,390
Shuhong,

644
00:37:59,970 --> 00:38:01,420
you must make sure our Baoquan

645
00:38:01,420 --> 00:38:02,750
looks good in the photo.

646
00:38:02,970 --> 00:38:04,490
Our Baoquan's a big shot!

647
00:38:04,780 --> 00:38:06,440
He can easily cause a stir

648
00:38:06,610 --> 00:38:08,710
and make the metropolis tremble.

649
00:38:09,650 --> 00:38:10,410
How about this?

650
00:38:10,410 --> 00:38:11,830
I have a 6-inch plate left.

651
00:38:11,830 --> 00:38:13,520
Would you like a photo
of you two together?

652
00:38:13,520 --> 00:38:16,300
Yes! That's a great idea!

653
00:38:17,220 --> 00:38:18,010
Baoquan,

654
00:38:18,450 --> 00:38:19,050
how long has it been

655
00:38:19,050 --> 00:38:21,050
since we last took a photo together?

656
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:22,480
This fan is quite nice.

657
00:38:23,260 --> 00:38:25,970
Ren Bonian's flower painting. That's rare.

658
00:38:26,610 --> 00:38:29,870
Don't just look at the painting.
There's calligraphy too.

659
00:38:30,450 --> 00:38:33,450
"If life could remain
the way it was when we first met."

660
00:38:34,700 --> 00:38:35,940
Nalan Xingde's poem.

661
00:38:37,950 --> 00:38:38,510
Okay.

662
00:39:17,130 --> 00:39:18,140
Chairman Song.

663
00:39:20,540 --> 00:39:21,630
Shuhong,

664
00:39:22,660 --> 00:39:24,190
these two stocks you bought

665
00:39:24,340 --> 00:39:25,600
have tripled in value.

666
00:39:26,780 --> 00:39:28,820
I felt they might drop
in the next few days,

667
00:39:28,820 --> 00:39:30,130
so I sold them for you.

668
00:39:32,450 --> 00:39:33,980
And what a coincidence that

669
00:39:34,300 --> 00:39:36,230
you happen to need money right now.

670
00:39:38,940 --> 00:39:40,480
Any news about my sister?

671
00:39:46,610 --> 00:39:47,450
But I've confirmed

672
00:39:47,450 --> 00:39:49,050
with the police station that

673
00:39:49,100 --> 00:39:50,300
your brother-in-law, Yang Yifan,

674
00:39:50,300 --> 00:39:51,990
was not one of the three under arrest.

675
00:39:51,990 --> 00:39:53,280
Thank God.

676
00:39:53,780 --> 00:39:55,240
That's really great news.

677
00:39:56,130 --> 00:39:57,090
I truly

678
00:39:57,120 --> 00:39:58,730
admire people like you.

679
00:39:59,460 --> 00:40:01,550
You've turned one into millions,

680
00:40:02,700 --> 00:40:04,590
sacrificing for the cause,

681
00:40:05,410 --> 00:40:06,570
fighting to the death,

682
00:40:06,570 --> 00:40:08,370
never-ending, never-ceasing.

683
00:40:08,580 --> 00:40:10,380
Thank you for seeing it that way.

684
00:40:11,300 --> 00:40:12,090
Shuhong,

685
00:40:12,700 --> 00:40:14,090
a young, pretty,

686
00:40:14,090 --> 00:40:16,300
and well-educated girl like you shouldn't

687
00:40:16,300 --> 00:40:17,610
lead an unsettled, chaotic life

688
00:40:17,610 --> 00:40:18,700
like this forever.

689
00:40:18,820 --> 00:40:19,880
Don't you think so?

690
00:40:20,090 --> 00:40:21,090
I'm fine,

691
00:40:21,220 --> 00:40:21,900
really.

692
00:40:22,570 --> 00:40:23,610
After all these years,

693
00:40:23,610 --> 00:40:25,610
it's my first time living by myself.

694
00:40:26,070 --> 00:40:27,200
Away from that man,

695
00:40:28,650 --> 00:40:31,420
I surprisingly feel so calm inside.

696
00:40:33,500 --> 00:40:35,030
You're referring to Mr. Wu?

697
00:40:36,940 --> 00:40:38,490
He's no ordinary man.

698
00:40:39,820 --> 00:40:40,880
You think he's extraordinary?

699
00:40:40,880 --> 00:40:41,590
Of course.

700
00:40:42,610 --> 00:40:43,610
Everyone in Shanghai's

701
00:40:43,610 --> 00:40:45,210
business world agrees on it.

702
00:40:45,420 --> 00:40:47,170
He's been involved in almost

703
00:40:47,570 --> 00:40:49,900
all those world-shaking feats.

704
00:40:50,380 --> 00:40:51,860
You all know about him?

705
00:40:52,220 --> 00:40:54,020
This is a century of revolution.

706
00:40:54,570 --> 00:40:56,010
No one can stay out of it.

707
00:40:58,710 --> 00:41:00,230
But why do I feel that

708
00:41:01,490 --> 00:41:04,020
he's becoming
more and more unapproachable?

709
00:41:04,620 --> 00:41:06,740
I could tell when you just
came to my house.

710
00:41:06,740 --> 00:41:08,540
Something so serious happened,

711
00:41:09,700 --> 00:41:11,780
yet I didn't see fear on your face.

712
00:41:12,180 --> 00:41:13,040
All I could see

713
00:41:13,490 --> 00:41:15,220
was a sense of loss and sadness.

714
00:41:17,700 --> 00:41:18,970
I'm very sad.

715
00:41:19,450 --> 00:41:20,580
Like, heartbroken.

716
00:41:21,940 --> 00:41:23,220
How did you two meet?

717
00:41:25,770 --> 00:41:26,770
It's a long story.

718
00:41:27,640 --> 00:41:29,310
Did he force you to accept him?

719
00:41:32,370 --> 00:41:33,670
Well, that's it.

720
00:41:34,070 --> 00:41:35,930
It was your own choice, wasn't it?

721
00:41:36,380 --> 00:41:37,380
I can understand.

722
00:41:37,500 --> 00:41:39,060
Compared to my son,

723
00:41:39,220 --> 00:41:41,050
a man like him is more exciting

724
00:41:41,680 --> 00:41:42,530
and appealing

725
00:41:42,940 --> 00:41:44,260
to girls.

726
00:41:44,940 --> 00:41:46,900
I can easily see the changes

727
00:41:47,170 --> 00:41:48,780
he has brought to you.

728
00:41:49,790 --> 00:41:51,180
I'm even thinking that

729
00:41:52,170 --> 00:41:53,700
it's hard to believe

730
00:41:55,530 --> 00:41:57,610
a girl like you

731
00:41:58,650 --> 00:41:59,940
is from Anqing.

732
00:42:00,260 --> 00:42:02,170
Song Chen is also embarking on this path.

733
00:42:02,170 --> 00:42:03,040
He and Mr. Wu

734
00:42:03,070 --> 00:42:04,400
hit it off immediately.

735
00:42:05,700 --> 00:42:07,530
That's because of you.

736
00:42:07,740 --> 00:42:09,010
I know my son.

737
00:42:09,380 --> 00:42:11,380
He only shows respect to rivals

738
00:42:11,380 --> 00:42:12,650
he can't defeat.

739
00:42:13,010 --> 00:42:14,220
You're not asking about him?

740
00:42:14,220 --> 00:42:15,550
What should I ask about?

741
00:42:15,970 --> 00:42:17,450
He only talks to me

742
00:42:17,450 --> 00:42:18,260
when he needs money.
